On the right side of the street, a row of trees stands tall, their leaves a vibrant green against the clear blue sky. The street itself is lined with power lines, a common sight in many urban areas. The overall color palette is dominated by shades of green from the trees and blue from the sky, creating a calm and peaceful atmosphere.
